						<xml xmlns="https://developers.google.com/blockly/xml"><block type="response_send" id="Hg9@Q`M#T2IG6KzyZv!#" x="150" y="170"><value name="NAME"><block type="text" id="pXli=!xh$EHFeVtL+d70"><field name="TEXT">Hola Mundo !!!</field></block></value></block></xml>
		responses: 

